Now, Aiden and Jackson, as the new leaders of the werewolf community, I understand your concerns. However, Finn's strength and cunning necessitate a united front. Your newfound abilities will undoubtedly serve us well, but remember, we must respect and value each member of our alliance.

My dear brother Elijah, you question my feelings for Hope, but my devotion to her is not in doubt. I am merely focused on ensuring her safety and controlling the prophecy that looms over us.

As for you, Kol, I am aware of your desire to indulge in mischief, but I implore you to exercise restraint. Your actions could jeopardize the progress we have made in mending our family's bonds.

And Marcel, your enthusiasm for literature is commendable, but I must attend to matters more pressing than serving as your audience. But fear not, your dedication to learning has not gone unnoticed.

In the end, I believe that our family will persevere, and we shall overcome any obstacle that stands in our way. Together, we will ensure the safety of Hope and maintain the balance in our beloved city.
